webpage.title: Software Engineer (Entry/Fresh Graduates)
webpage.description: The National Instruments Semiconductor BU Systems R&D team has an immediate opening for a Software Engineer. We are looking at candidates who are open to work in LabVIEW, C# or Python in a dynamic environment with close interactions with customers and offering managers within the BU. This position will focus primarily on mixed-signal validation test application architectures for large scale parallel SMU test systems, mixed signal IC power validation and LCR device level measurements. Defining validation procedures for common mixed signal blocks such as data converters (ADC/DAC), voltage regulators (LDOs and Switchers), and interface protocols. In this role, the Systems R&D Engineer will provide subject matter expertise for customer DUTs and system architectural design guidance for Automated Design Validation solutions.
